{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TimeInterval","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSTimeInterval","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Animation","text":"Animation","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnimationV","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"delay","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The number of seconds to delay the start of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An animation with a delayed start."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to delay the start of an animation. For example, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"following code animates the height change of two capsules."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Animation of the first "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Capsule","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" begins immediately. However,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation of the second one doesn’t begin until a half second later."}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct ContentView: View {","    @State private var adjustBy = 100.0","","    var body: some View